## When to Use

**Use EasyLM if you want:**
- Râ€‘style regression output in Python  
- Easy model comparison  
- Teaching/learning regression concepts  
- Clean, extensible code  

**Use alternatives when you need:**
- Production ML pipelines â†’ scikitâ€‘learn  
- Advanced econometrics â†’ statsmodels  
- Deep learning â†’ TensorFlow/PyTorch  

