## Roadmap

**Version 1.0 (Current)**  
- Basic OLS regression  
- R-style summaries  
- Model comparison  
- Visualization tools  

**Version 1.1 (Planned)**  
- Weighted least squares  
- Ridge & Lasso regression  
- Cross-validation utilities  
- Polynomial features  

**Version 2.0 (Future)**  
- Generalized Linear Models (GLM)  
- Time series regression  
- Mixed effects models  
- Interactive web dashboard  
